00:15:25.880 --> 00:15:32.880
Obviously the entertainment company, which I've taken over from my dad and my grandfather, where originally that was just dancers.

00:15:32.880 --> 00:15:37.880
We now do the full entertainment packages going into wedding event management as well now.

00:15:37.880 --> 00:15:42.880
Dance floors, DJs, drummers, singers, jazz players, you name it, PA hire.

00:15:42.880 --> 00:15:51.880
That's the entertainment side of technology company based in China, property companies based in India and in the UK.

00:15:51.880 --> 00:15:54.880
So, yeah, loads of little things that's keeping us busy and out of trouble.

00:15:54.880 --> 00:16:03.880
John and Raj, thank you so much for that insight, not mainly into the role of the dole and bungering, part of Carnival,

00:16:03.880 --> 00:16:18.880
